             Applicable only if the fsIpDbBindingType is DHCP."
    ::= { fsMIIpDbBindingEntry 7 }

    fsMIIpDbHostBindingID OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX      Unsigned32
        MAX-ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS      current
        DESCRIPTION
